 item and look back fondly on the quest.  With TLC in place one cannot roleplay.  One MUST go to spoiler sites and figure out when quests will no longer be available to them, buy items from players, or bother some player to do it for you.  <br>
<br>
Personally i want to be left alone, do things by myself, and not be forced to buy items from some snivelling worm who wants the world for them.  A guild? Why? I wish to have peace and quiet, not be forced or guilted into doing things for people on the little free time I have.  If I want to do that I play my main, which I do the majority of the time anyhow.  If I want a change I come to fv.<br>
<br>
TLC and the removal of the no drop tag is just a way for newbs and lowbs to extort cash from high level players.  &quot;Oh good, now the newb and lowb can farm items instead! Man is TLC progressive thinking!&quot; <br>
<br>
One word...RIDICULOUS. <p><img src="http://members.fortunecity.com/samslade/shadcon/Images/wizard.jpg" width="150" height="150"><BR>

