I'm sorry to disagree with you here.  I do quite well roleplaying (IMHO) with TLC.  And, I can do the quests, regardless of reward or not as well.  If I really find something I &quot;need&quot; and cannot get, there are those willing to sell, those willing to trade, or those willing to be hired to obtain it.<br>
